{"tid":1508268,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"FAA警告:  不得對無人機進行武器化改裝","createTime":"2019-08-26T13:00:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T14:20:26.000Z","uid":66271,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"968949fffaebb2e741662f976a11c7ea9aa6e379","tid":1508268,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T13:00:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?resize=2000%2C2000%2Cshrink&amp;image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2019-08%2F7f5a4930-c7cc-11e9-aa7d-f1db60b31bc4&amp;client=a1acac3e1b3290917d92&amp;signature=3017c4cb3d98d045d8c1e3ddd1f8472cf4a28af9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fo.aolcdn.com%2Fimages%2Fdims%3Fresize%3D2000%252C2000%252Cshrink%26image_uri%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fs.yimg.com%252Fos%252Fcreatr-uploaded-images%252F2019-08%252F7f5a4930-c7cc-11e9-aa7d-f1db60b31bc4%26client%3Da1acac3e1b3290917d92%26signature%3D3017c4cb3d98d045d8c1e3ddd1f8472cf4a28af9&h=548cac90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n把無人機改造成武器的行為很危險，相信這在許多人腦中應該是不用特別去強調的常識。但很顯然美國 FAA 看到的情況並非如此，要不然他們也不會專門針對這種做法去特意發佈一條警告了。日前 FAA 在自己的網站上刊登公告強調，武器化無人機會違反他們的規定，由此帶來的後果亦可能觸犯聯邦或美國各州的法律。「這對人身安全和你的銀行帳戶都會帶來巨大打擊。」FAA 如此寫道，並進一步表示違規者可能將面臨最高 2.5 萬美元的罰款。<br />\n<br />\n實際上，在美國擅自給無人機加裝武器的例子此前已經出現過不少，很難說是哪件事讓 FAA 覺得有必要在這個時間點上警示大眾。但不管怎麼說，既然有潛在的風險，那監管機構有預警意識總會多少給提高安全性帶來幫助吧。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4880793e9d5f19b361815d541cc8e5c024c7f945","tid":1508268,"uid":198008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T13:03:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02cdfb75a2ac3108bcf8896da509f2c2e7cdc789","tid":1508268,"uid":33930,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T13:18:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4B5ZOzj.gif